The team lineups for the Euro 2012
final between Spain and Italy in Kiev, Ukraine. Kickoff is
9:45pm local time -- click {IC2 <GO>} for time converter:  Spain: Casillas, Pique, Ramos, Arbeloa, Alba, Iniesta,
Xavi, Fabregas, Alonso, Busquets, Silva.  Substitutes: Valdes, Reina, Albiol, Martinez, Juanfran, Cazorla,
Navas, Rodriguez, Torres, Negredo, Mata, Llorente.  Italy: Buffon, Chiellini, Abate, Barzagli, Bonucci,
Marchisio,  De Rossi , Montolivo, Pirlo, Balotelli, Cassano.  Substitutes: Sirigu, De Sanctis, Maggio, Ogbonna, Balzaretti,
Motta, Giaccherini, Diamanti, Nocerino, Di Natale, Borini,
Giovinco.  REFEREE: Pedro Proenca (Portugal)  --James Cone at the London Sports Desk +44-20-7673-2572 or at
 jcone@bloomberg.net .
 